Retirement Income Option  / About Great-West Life & Annuity Insurance Company
Great-West SecureFoundation®
  
About Great-West Life & Annuity Insurance Company
Great-West SecureFoundation®  — Backed by Great-West Life & Annuity Insurance Company

After the financial crisis in the late 2000's, the way people began thinking about
and planning for retirement changed. Suddenly, the company behind an
investment became as important as how an investment performed. Trust,
credibility and strength took on new importance for investors.


        We recognize that our actions as a company can have a long-term effect on
your retirement. It's something that's guided our approach to
business since the Great-West Family of Companies* got their start with
The Great-West Life Assurance Company in 1891. For over 100 years, we've
helped our clients through challenging economic times by doing business
the right way. Great-West Life & Annuity Insurance Company is a leading
provider of employer-sponsored retirement savings plans. We also provide
annuity and life insurance products for individuals, families and businesses.

        Even though the Great-West Family of Companies has been around a
long time, we are also an innovative company. Markets change. People's
needs change. We have to change to meet those needs. Offering Great-West SecureFoundation®  is a good
example. Many people are looking for a way to protect their future,
long-term retirement income from market losses, while benefiting from
market gains. They want to stay invested when markets go up. And they
want retirement income for the long term. That's why we at Empower Retirement developed and are proud to offer
quality products such as Great-West SecureFoundation. With Great-West
SecureFoundation, we are continuing our long history of conservative,
disciplined risk management. 
        
      

        Great-West Life & Annuity Insurance Company is rated by independent, nationally recognized rating organizations that regularly review and analyze the financial strength and creditworthiness of the company. We have consistently received high marks from industry sources for financial strength. 
      

        Great-West Life & Annuity Insurance Company's financial strength and stability is typified by the strong ratings given by major ratings agencies. 
 


